{"tid":2441894,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"飛往月球：日本富豪前澤友作公開徵友繞月飛行","createTime":"2021-03-11T04:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T06:14:37.000Z","uid":248270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7289ffc84a6d1eeecced59fcbdfeb5e381f127df","tid":2441894,"uid":248270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKSZgVz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKSZgVz.png&h=252d01e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OP0_4rzPZcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOP0_4rzPZcA&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b7cb0138\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OP0_4rzPZcA</a><br />\n<br />\n日本億萬富商前澤友作公開徵求8名伙伴和他一起前往太空進行繞月旅行。<br />\n<br />\n前澤友作在推特上發表視頻表示，「我歡迎各種背景的人加入」，他還在貼文中附上申請細節的鏈接。<br />\n<br />\n他說他已經購買了繞月旅行的整個行程，因此想要加入他的人不需要另外支付費用，就可以和他一起登上伊隆&middot;馬斯克（Elon Musk）的太空探索技術公司（SpaceX）發射的星際火箭繞月球飛行。<br />\n前澤友作將這趟繞月飛行稱為「親愛的月球」計劃，預計在2023年成行<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56271535.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-56271535.amp&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=c2a40d6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-56271535.amp&h=18ae429f\" target=\"_blank\">www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56271535.amp</a>"},{"pid":"7173076a9b712c6e9daf630b904124e4a9793a35","tid":2441894,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"無重力屌西我都想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95856ef19262dc919b4fb765b400e7c32f5e82fc","tid":2441894,"uid":210778,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7173076a9b712c6e9daf630b9